title: CHIANG MAI Digital Nomads Capital
body:
Whatever you want to call it - digital nomad, location independent or (as my mother calls it) aimless laptop hobo for a few years now. There’s a lot of misinformation and useless advice about the lifestyle and how to get there. For an (entirely free) A->Z plan (bonus: it’s an audiobook so you don’t even have to read it) check out: https://digitalnomadblr.tumblr.com/serve-no-master-audiobook

LYDIA ISNANTO VLOG EPISODE 39JUNE 2017 - CHIANG MAI, THAILANDThis is part my VLOG series about Digital Nomads lifestyle, where we can use wireless internet, smartphones and cloud-based applications to work remotely wherever we live or travel. It’s not for everyone, but if you love flexibility, then it might be a good fit because a life of adventure can be cheaper & more productive than staying home. A nomadic lifestyle has been an effective way to live while building a company for many startup entrepreneurs, online marketers, sales, mobile/web developers, hardcore programmers, graphic/media designers, podcasters, bloggers, photographers, filmmakers, writers, lawyers, and venture capitalists.This video is not sponsored or endorsed by any brand or organization and all opinions are entirely mine.GEARS THAT I USE FOR THIS VLOG :-Ztylus Revolver Kit RV-3http://ztylus.refr.cc/6TLHZBW-Go Pro Hero 5 BlackShoot in 2.7K 30fps reduced to 1080 in this videoSlow Motion shoot in 1080 120fpshttps://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B01…-AiBird Uoplay Universal 3-Axis Stabilizer for Smartphones & Go Prohttps://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B01…-iPHONE 7 Plus (Shoot in 4K reduced to 1080 in this video)https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B01…-MANFROTTO MTPIXI-B PIXI Mini Tripodhttps://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00…-JOBY GORILLA POD Action Video Tripodhttps://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00…-Selfie Stick EDITING SOFTWARE : ADOBE PREMIERE PRO CChttps://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00…DISCLAIMER: This video and description contains affiliate links, which means that if you click on one of the product links, I’ll receive a small commission. Chocolate cake-in-a-mug 🤤🍫

So, little student tip for ya. When I was tidying and was living with my...
caption:
SWIPE FOR RECIPE 👉🏼👉🏼👉🏼

Chocolate cake-in-a-mug 🤤🍫

So, little student tip for ya. When I was tidying and was living with my brother and pretty tight for cash, I’d buy these ingredients, and when ever I wanted a treat (which is 99% of the time chocolate) I’d whip this up and it really is pretty filling! The ingredients last am age and I feel like surely it’s cost effective?? I haven’t actually worked it out though. 🤷🏼‍♀️

I have become a master at cake-in-a-mugs and love being simple with a dusting of icing sugar on top. You can defos add other things; a spoon of Nutella in the middle, mixing in some crumbled up Oreos? Sprinkles? Anything you fancy 😍

Pleaseeeee if you make this, send my a pic 🙏🏼 (I’ll probably end up making one myself… even though I already made myself one today) 😂

blog.description: Hello, I'm John/Mist! I'm a disabled transgender artist from the UK. I am the Mangle, the Mangle is me! My Art: Commissions are open! | Drop me an ask for more info and check my art tag to see some of my work! I greatly appreciate any support you can throw my way to help cover the cost of my medications and getting back on T which I've been unable to afford for the last 2 years My Patreon | My Ko-Fi Page | PayPal donations My Blog: Tumblr has decided boobs are yesterday's news so where once there were cosplays you'll now find mostly my fandom-related art, rambling and memetastic posts. Fandom slave to: Runaways, Spiderverse, MCU (and Marvel in general), Venom, Homestuck, Animal Crossing, Five Nights at Freddy's, She-Ra (SPoP and MOTU), Gorillaz, Splatoon, Arms, Doctor Who, Red Dwarf, Black Mirror, Guardians of the Galaxy, Deadpool, Cloverfield, Ashes to Ashes, Life on Mars, Pokemon, DHMIS, Hiveswap, Legend of Zelda, classic Sonic, 80s and 90s nostalgia, fun and games from the Highly Medicated Corner and nutty shenannigans with my betrothed beautiful fiancee and lovely partner Lucy :) About Me: I'm a transguy who enjoys cross dressing for cosplays, I live on a boat, I'm demisexual and am SO super lucky to have found my Moirspritmaterail, best friend, lover, soul mate, lovely partner for life ❤️💛💚💙💜 I am xX-Misty on FFnet and Fictionpress.
